No. 884,

Mise.

Cachoian v. United States. Solicitor General Griswold, Assistant Attorney General Vinson, and Jerome M. Feit for the United States.

C. A. 2d Cir. Motion for leave to supplement petition granted. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Marshall took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and petition.
